==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irresponsible
<hw>Ir`re*spon"si*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ir-</ets> not + <ets>responsible</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>irresponsable</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not responsible; not
liable or able to answer for consequences; innocent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not to be trusted; unreliable; lacking a proper
sense of responsibility.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>irresponsibleness</ent>⟦br⟧
